	PR ld/5526
	* elf-bfd.h (eh_cie_fde): Add u.cie.u.full_cie and u.cie.merged
	fields.  Rename u.cie.u.merged to u.cie.u.merged_with.
	(eh_frame_sec_info): Add a cies field.
